  "detailed_description": "DepthQVR_AQUA is a fun, engaging, immersive ride & casual gaming experience, a layered experiential environment filled with intuitive interaction, story immersion, and exhilaration. <br><br>This novel application of virtual reality technology simulates a traditional indoor amusement ride on which passengers aboard a guided vehicle travel through specially lit scenes that typically contain video, animation, sound, music, game interactives, and special effects. <br><br>We support Steam VR and 'Desktop' (non VR) gameplay modes; 'Desktop' is supported via Keyboard/Mouse and Xbox Controller.<br><br>The AQUA themeology is a gaming skin, a stage dress that sits atop our evolving and entertaining game mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/502f4538c45947950b02b4fb1be3b034.poster.avif?t=1632209014\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/502f4538c45947950b02b4fb1be3b034.webm?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/502f4538c45947950b02b4fb1be3b034.mp4?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The addition of optional motion simulation technology transforms DepthQVR® into a realistic ride experience for out-of-home PC Café, Entertainment Attractions, Brand Experiences, and Educational Attractions. The ride's immersive participatory nature, playful ‘natural-touch’ interactivity, and exhilarating body motion surprises and delights viewers of all ages, sparking lasting memories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/fad2d95fa0470452882e9562e50e4098.poster.avif?t=1632209014\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/fad2d95fa0470452882e9562e50e4098.webm?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/fad2d95fa0470452882e9562e50e4098.mp4?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/47fa96ab29bf6fc96005fd4915b8f27f.poster.avif?t=1632209014\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/47fa96ab29bf6fc96005fd4915b8f27f.webm?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/47fa96ab29bf6fc96005fd4915b8f27f.mp4?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "DepthQVR_AQUA is a fun, engaging, immersive ride & casual gaming experience, a layered experiential environment filled with intuitive interaction, story immersion, and exhilaration. <br><br>This novel application of virtual reality technology simulates a traditional indoor amusement ride on which passengers aboard a guided vehicle travel through specially lit scenes that typically contain video, animation, sound, music, game interactives, and special effects. <br><br>We support Steam VR and 'Desktop' (non VR) gameplay modes; 'Desktop' is supported via Keyboard/Mouse and Xbox Controller.<br><br>The AQUA themeology is a gaming skin, a stage dress that sits atop our evolving and entertaining game mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/502f4538c45947950b02b4fb1be3b034.poster.avif?t=1632209014\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/502f4538c45947950b02b4fb1be3b034.webm?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/502f4538c45947950b02b4fb1be3b034.mp4?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The addition of optional motion simulation technology transforms DepthQVR® into a realistic ride experience for out-of-home PC Café, Entertainment Attractions, Brand Experiences, and Educational Attractions. The ride's immersive participatory nature, playful ‘natural-touch’ interactivity, and exhilarating body motion surprises and delights viewers of all ages, sparking lasting memories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/fad2d95fa0470452882e9562e50e4098.poster.avif?t=1632209014\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/fad2d95fa0470452882e9562e50e4098.webm?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/fad2d95fa0470452882e9562e50e4098.mp4?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/47fa96ab29bf6fc96005fd4915b8f27f.poster.avif?t=1632209014\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/47fa96ab29bf6fc96005fd4915b8f27f.webm?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1026760/extras/47fa96ab29bf6fc96005fd4915b8f27f.mp4?t=1632209014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
